Best wow tricks
Use these sparingly:

Zoom from galaxy → system → planet → surface marker in one uninterrupted camera move.

Planet wakes up on hover with atmosphere brightening and orbit lines sharpening.

Night/day terminator slowly crossing the planet so city lights appear naturally.

Cloud parallax moving at a different speed from the surface.

Lens bloom only on stars, beacons and major reflections, not everywhere.

Data storms around unstable repos.

Soft ambient audio zones per system for mood and feedback.

